title: History Extra podcast - March 2011
itunes:title: History Extra podcast - March 2011
itunes:subtitle: Harry Bennett discusses the role of the Merchant Navy in the Battle of the Atlantic, Niall Ferguson considers how much longer western supremacy can last, and Edward Higgs explores the challenges of the Victorian census.
